# EmailJS (https://www.emailjs.com)
# 1. Sign up at emailjs.com with your Gmail / college account
# 2. Add a Gmail email service  →  copy the Service ID here
# 3. Create ONE template with:
#      To Email  : {{to_email}}
#      Subject   : {{subject}}
#      Body (HTML): {{{message_html}}}   ← triple braces = raw HTML
#    Copy the Template ID here
# 4. Go to Account → API Keys and copy the Public Key here
